readable.content: A white dog and two black dogs playing A white poodle and 2 black poodles are playing on the grass . A white poodle and two black poodles are playing in the grass on an autumn day . A white poodle is climbing over a black poodle , who is in turn climbing over another black poodle . Two black dogs and one white dog interact .
